	* src/fmshaper_own.cpp, src/fmshaper_own.h: Cosmetic, spaces are
	  allowed in match files.

2008-03-14 16:26  oeildepierre

	* src/fmshaper_own.cpp, src/mainviewwidget.cpp: Unicode ranges
	  combo is now regenerated if it sticks to an empty range

2008-03-12 14:16  oeildepierre

	* src/application.qrc, src/fmotf.cpp, src/fmotf.h,
	  src/fmshaper_own.cpp, src/fontitem.cpp, src/langs/deva.dict,
	  src/langs/deva.match: Ease developpement of match files
	  You can set a ShaperDataDir in
	  ~/.config/Undertype/fontmatrix.conf which will override the
	  resource dir so you don’t need to rebuild to see changes in your
	  own match file nor re-run Fontmatrix

