2008-02-23 21:21  oeildepierre

	* src/CMakeLists.txt, src/fmrepair.cpp, src/fmrepair.h,
	  src/fontitem.cpp, src/fontitem.h, src/mainviewwidget.cpp,
	  src/repair.ui, src/typotek.cpp, src/typotek.h: Fixed
	  impossibility to activate different fonts with the same file name
	  but in different directories - links are now prefixed with the
	  target file size.
	  It means that you won’t be able to deactivate your fonts with
	  fontmatrix, sorry.
	  It also fixed problem with no detection of the AFM files.
	  Added the mockup of the "check database" dialog

