2008-01-19 17:48  oeildepierre

	* src/dataloader.cpp, src/dataloader.h, src/fontitem.cpp,
	  src/savedata.cpp, src/typotek.cpp, src/typotek.h: Files and
	  directories schema changed:
	  $home/.fonts-reserved/fonts.data becomes $home/.fontmatrix.data
	  $home/.fonts-reserved disappears as font files are no more
	  copied, .fontmatrix.data
	  now tracks down _absolute_ file paths.

